data.name: sshCommand_DRAM
data.value: echo 1 | { sudo -S dmidecode -t 17 | awk -F":" '/Type:/{print $2;exit;}'; free -h|awk '/^Память:/{print $2}'; } | xargs

data.name: sshCommand_SystemInfo
data.value: echo "Имя системы" hostname echo "Процессор" cat /proc/cpuinfo | awk -F":" '/model name/{print $2;exit;}' echo "Материнская плата" dmidecode -t 2 | awk -F":" '/Manufacturer:/, /Product Name:/{print $2}' echo "Оперативная память" echo 1 | { sudo -S dmidecode -t 17 | awk -F":" '/Type:/{print $2;exit;}'; free -h|awk '/^Память:/{print $2}'; } | xargs echo "Жесткий диск" echo 1 | sudo -S hdparm -I /dev/sda | awk -F'[()]' '/GB/{print $2}'

data.name: sshCommand_SystemInfo2
data.value: echo "Имя системы" HN="$(hostname)" echo $HN echo "Процессор" CPU="$(cat /proc/cpuinfo | awk -F":" '/model name/{print $2;exit;}')" echo $CPU echo "Материнская плата" MB="$(echo $TempPass | sudo -S dmidecode -t 2 | awk -F":" '/Manufacturer:/, /Product Name:/{print $2}')" echo $MB echo "Оперативная память" MEMORY="$(echo $TempPass | { sudo -S dmidecode -t 17 | awk -F":" '/Type:/{print $2;exit;}'; free -h|awk '/^Память:/{print $2}'; } | xargs)" echo $MEMORY echo "Жесткий диск" HDD="$(echo $TempPass | sudo -S hdparm -I /dev/sda | awk -F'[()]' '/GB/{print $2}')" echo $HDD

data.name: sshCommand_ClearMotion
data.value: echo 'До чистки Motion' df -h echo echo 'Выполняется уменьшение архива Motion до 20 дней' echo $TempPass|sudo -S find /home/.motion \( -name "*.avi" -o -name "*.ogg" \) -mtime +20 -type f -exec rm -rf {} \; echo echo 'После чистки Motion' df -h

data.name: sshCommand_SmartCtl
data.value: echo $TempPass|sudo -S su apt-get install smartmontools fdisk -l smartctl -a /dev/sda

data.name: sshCommand_TEST
data.value: df -h echo $TempPass|sudo -S find /home/.motion \( -name "*.avi" -o -name "*.ogg" \) -mtime +20 -type f -exec rm -rf {} \; df -h history -c df -h echo $TempPass|sudo -S find /home/.motion \( -name "*.avi" -o -name "*.ogg" \) -mtime +20 -type f -exec rm -rf {} \; df -h history -c
